HEADWORD: Messidor
<hw>Mes`si`dor"</hw> <pr>(F. ?; E. ?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.,
fr. L. <ets>messis</ets> harvest.]</ety> <def>The tenth month of the
French republican calendar dating from September 22, 1792. It began June
19, and ended July 18. See <er>Vend⟦eacute⟧miaire</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

